'''麦迪逊大道550号'''（{{lang-en|550 Madison Avenue}}），原名'''索尼大厦'''（Sony Tower）、'''索尼广场'''（Sony Plaza）、'''AT&T大厦'''（AT&T Building），是一栋高{{Convert|647|ft|m|0}} 、37层的摩天大楼，位于[[纽约市|纽约市]][[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]][[麦迪逊大道|麦迪逊大道]]550号，介于55街、56街之间<ref>{{cite web|title=Sony Tower|url=http://www.emporis.com/en/wm/bu/?id=sonytower-newyorkcity-ny-usa|publisher=Emporis.com|accessdate=July 12, 2008|archive-date=2008-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080317205951/http://www.emporis.com/en/wm/bu/?id=sonytower-newyorkcity-ny-usa|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它曾是[[索尼美国|索尼美国]]公司的总部<ref name="bbcsale2013">{{cite news| url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-21073668 |title= Sony sells Manhattan headquarters skyscraper for $1.1bn |date= January 18, 2013  | publisher= [[BBC_News|BBC News]] | accessdate= January 18, 2013| quote= The firm will also record a windfall profit in its accounts, as the building is being sold at a gain of £685m, compared with the price that Sony originally paid for it in 2002. The firm said that it will continue to lease the building back for another three years following the sale, which is expected to be completed in March.  The skyscraper houses 1,500 Sony employees, including its music and films businesses.}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|publisher =Prospect Magazine |title= Postmodernism is dead |url= http://www.prospectmagazine.co.uk/2011/07/postmodernism-is-dead-va-exhibition-age-of-authenticism/ | date= July 20, 2011 | accessdate=January 18, 2013}}</ref>。

